</head>
<body>

     <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen md:flex-row container mx-auto w-[50vw] md:min-h-0 md:h-[70vh] space-x-10 mt-20 mb-40">
        <!-- movie picture container -->
        <div class="w-full h-auto flex justify-center container mx-auto md:mx-0">
          <img src="../images/Films/blade-runner.png" class="object-cover h-full" alt="movie picture">
      </div>
        
        <!-- movie detail -->
        <div class="container flex flex-col h-full w-[40vw] justify-center items-start space-y-6 py-5 ">
          <!-- movie title -->
          <h1 class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold md:text-4xl text-center text-xl ml-4 md:ml-0">
            Blade Runner
          </h1>

          <!-- movie score button-->
          <div class="w-28 h-12 bg-redOne p-1 space-x-2 flex items-center justify-center group  ml-8 md:ml-0">
            <div class="mb-0.5">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 128 128"><path fill="#fdd835" d="m68.05 7.23l13.46 30.7a7.047 7.047 0 0 0 5.82 4.19l32.79 2.94c3.71.54 5.19 5.09 2.5 7.71l-24.7 20.75c-2 1.68-2.91 4.32-2.36 6.87l7.18 33.61c.63 3.69-3.24 6.51-6.56 4.76L67.56 102a7.033 7.033 0 0 0-7.12 0l-28.62 16.75c-3.31 1.74-7.19-1.07-6.56-4.76l7.18-33.61c.54-2.55-.36-5.19-2.36-6.87L5.37 52.78c-2.68-2.61-1.2-7.17 2.5-7.71l32.79-2.94a7.047 7.047 0 0 0 5.82-4.19l13.46-30.7c1.67-3.36 6.45-3.36 8.11-.01"/><path fill="#ffff8d" d="m67.07 39.77l-2.28-22.62c-.09-1.26-.35-3.42 1.67-3.42c1.6 0 2.47 3.33 2.47 3.33l6.84 18.16c2.58 6.91 1.52 9.28-.97 10.68c-2.86 1.6-7.08.35-7.73-6.13"/><path fill="#f4b400" d="M95.28 71.51L114.9 56.2c.97-.81 2.72-2.1 1.32-3.57c-1.11-1.16-4.11.51-4.11.51l-17.17 6.71c-5.12 1.77-8.52 4.39-8.82 7.69c-.39 4.4 3.56 7.79 9.16 3.97"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="font-arvo text-white text-xl font-bold">
              5 <span class="text-sm">/ 5</span> 
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- movie info -->
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 text-sm">

            <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
              <div class="mb-1 flex items-center">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="text-blueOne" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.277 4.781A4 4 0 0 1 14.606 3h.213a2 2 0 0 1 1.973 2.329L16.18 9h2.38a3 3 0 0 1 2.942 3.588l-1.2 6A3 3 0 0 1 17.36 21H6a3 3 0 0 1-3-3v-8a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3.93a1 1 0 0 0 .832-.445zM7 11H5v7a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-blueOne font-arvo font-bold text-xs md:text-sm">248</p>
            </div>

            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold text-xs md:text-sm">1h31</p>
            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold text-xs md:text-sm">Science-fiction</p>

          </div>

          <div class="container text-nowrap flex flex-col text-xs ml-7 md:ml-0">
            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold">Sortie : 01 mai 2024</p>
            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold block md:hidden">
                Avec Ryan Gosling,<br> Harrison Ford,<br> de Denis Villeneuve
              </p>
              <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne font-bold hidden md:block md:text-xs">
                Avec Ryan Gosling, Harrison Ford, de Denis Villeneuve
              </p>
          </div>

          <div class="container">
            <p class="font-arvo text-blueOne w-full md:w-[70%]">
              En 2049, la société est fragilisée par les nombreuses tensions entre les humains et leurs esclaves créés par bio-ingénierie. L'officier K est un blade runner: il fait partie d'une force...
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- movie reservation button -->
           <a href="/reservation/Choisir-sceance">
             <button class="w-44 h-16 bg-goldOne p-1 space-x-2 flex items-center justify-center group hover:scale-95 duration-200 ease-out">
               <p class="font-arvo text-white text-xl font-bold">
                 Réserver
               </p>
             </button>
           </a>

        </div>

      </div>
